&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Provide health and wellness group coaching to members in a virtual group setting to promote positive lifestyle habits and behaviors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Support members to develop self-directed strategies for sustainable, healthy lifestyle behavior change&lt;/li&gt;
