&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Follow program guidance and policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ensure members are informed of what to expect when engaging in coaching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Work under the general supervision of a Coaching Program Manager (or designee), who establishes objectives and priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
