&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At least 3 years of experience facilitating live virtual group coaching sessions for adults focused on sustainable weight management and behavior change&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong knowledge of behavior change principles, motivational interviewing, and other evidence-based coaching approaches&lt;/li&gt;
